'''Boga Minawk''' was a sport played in [[Repulsorlift/Legends|anti-gravity]], popular at the height of the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]]. There were many Boga Minawk enthusiasts at the [[Dona Laza]] [[Tapcafe/Legends|tapcafe]].

